## NDA / CONFIDENTIALITY AGREEMENT
Before producing the output, evaluate each of the following clauses:
Typical clauses include:

• Definition of Confidential Information
• Exclusions from Confidential Information
• Obligations of Receiving Party
• Permitted Disclosures
• Return or Destruction of Information
• Term and Survival of Obligations
• Remedies for Breach
• Assignment
• Governing Law and Jurisdiction
• Entire Agreement / Miscellaneous
• Non-Solicitation (sometimes included)

For each clause determine if it is PRESENT or ABSENT.
Only include ABSENT clauses in the final output.

